snippet.title: Command and Conquer: Intro Movie
snippet.description: I played the gold edition of Command & Conquer. Let's watch the intro movie without commentary. The NOD campaign is much harder. The first seven missions can be completed very fast and the others are not so easy. Now sit back and enjoy the intro and the following NOD walkthrough of the RTS godfather that starts a new genre in video game history!
